{
    "T06n1333u_001:0": " Cittatatvasaṅgrahaḥ",
    "T06n1333u_001:1": " namas tasmai bhagavate'rhate samyaksambuddhāya",
    "T06n1333u_001:2": " agraḥ śreṣṭaś ca jyeṣṭhas tribhuvanajagataś­ śāstṛbhūtaś ca loke",
    "T06n1333u_001:3": " yo'bhūl lakṣmīghanas tat padakamalayugam­ mastakenabhivandya",
    "T06n1333u_001:4": " lokānāṃ dlrghakālam pihitamaviditaṃ­ cittadharmasya tatvaṃ",
    "T06n1333u_001:5": " jijñāsūnām pravakṣye sugatamunimatam­ gauraveṇanugamya |",
    "T06n1333u_001:6": " ī. sarvā cittakathā dharme - proktaivādityabandhunā",
    "T06n1333u_001:7": " caturbhir eva vacanaiḥ - pañcaskandhādidarśane |",
    "T06n1333u_001:8": " 2. prathamā vedanā tatra - saṃjñā tu syād dvitlyīkā",
    "T06n1333u_001:9": " tṛtīyas tu ca saṃskāras - turyaṃ vijñānam eva hi |",
    "T06n1333u_001:10": " 3. etaccatuṣṭayaṃ yatrai - katvena gṛhyate yadā",
    "T06n1333u_001:11": " tadā tasya samūhasya - vayaṃ cittaṃ vadāmahe |",
    "T06n1333u_001:12": " 4. vedanā-saṃjñā-saṃskārāḥ - prabuddhasya gatir bhavet",
    "T06n1333u_001:13": " caturthaṃ tu ca vijñānaṃ - susuptasya bhaved gatiḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:14": " 5. avasthāhyantarbūtā tu - svapnaṃ evetyudīritā",
    "T06n1333u_001:15": " gatis tasyām prabuddhasya - susuptiś ca na vidyate |",
    "T06n1333u_001:16": " 6. prabuddhasya gatis tatra - kriyavjñānameva hi",
    "T06n1333u_001:17": " anyad akriyavijñānaṃ - susuptasya gatiḥ punaḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:18": " 7. avasthām antarbhūtām tu - dvayamiśravaśād viduḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:19": " atītasṃṛtisaṃskāra - rūpenāvirbhavantite",
    "T06n1333u_001:20": " 8. indriyārthasanṇikarṣāj - janyaṃ jñānaṃ tu vedanā",
    "T06n1333u_001:21": " upalabdhiś ca pratyakṣo - viṣayānubhavo'pi ca",
    "T06n1333u_001:22": " vedanāyās tu paryāyā - dṛśyante nyāyadarśane |",
    "T06n1333u_001:23": " 9. vedanāśabdasyārthasya - ṛgvede caiva saṃskṛte",
    "T06n1333u_001:24": " sambuddhena prayuktārtha - samaṃ kiñcin na dṛśyate |",
    "T06n1333u_001:25": " 10. vīthivijñānatraividhye - vedanā prathamābhavet",
    "T06n1333u_001:26": " saivarjujñānamārgaṃ syād - anye dye'nṛjuke tathā |",
    "T06n1333u_001:27": " 11. vīthivijñānasaṃjñā tu - cintanārthaṃ prakāśate",
    "T06n1333u_001:28": " tarkānumānajānana - sarvaṃjñāgataṃ bhavet |",
    "T06n1333u_001:29": " 12. vedanānāmapratyakso - vṛddhiṃ gaccati cintane",
    "T06n1333u_001:30": " dṛṣṭismṛtipsāsarve tu - saṃjñasādhakahetavaḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:31": " 13. vedanāsaṃjñāyugalam - ekaikaṃ hi prabhāsvaram",
    "T06n1333u_001:32": " prabhāsvaracittakathā - dharme tasmād dhi dṛśyate |",
    "T06n1333u_001:33": " 14. aprabhāsvaracittan tu - saṃskārasahitaṃ bhavet",
    "T06n1333u_001:34": " bāladarakacittaṃ hi - tasmād evāprabhāsvaram |",
    "T06n1333u_001:35": " 15. vedanāsaṃjñāvijñāna - saṃskārā buddhadarśane",
    "T06n1333u_001:36": " dṛṣṭārthayuktāḥ kutrāpi - dṛśyante nānyadarśane |",
    "T06n1333u_001:37": " 16. vedanāsaṃjñāsaṃskāra - trayaiḥ śabdair udīritam",
    "T06n1333u_001:38": " cittasya vīthivijñānam - muninādityabandhunā |",
    "T06n1333u_001:39": " 17. saṃskārakṣayaśabdārthaṃ - nirvāṇañ ca samam bhavet",
    "T06n1333u_001:40": " visaṃskāragataṃ cittam - iti buddhaprakāśanam |",
    "T06n1333u_001:41": " 18. saṃskāratṛṣṇāsambandhaḥ - katham jñātuṃ hi śakyate",
    "T06n1333u_001:42": " buddha evāvadat tatra - tṛṣṇānāṃ kṣayam adhyagām |",
    "T06n1333u_001:43": " 19. vyākṛtā'nivrtas tatra - tṛṣṇādoṣās trayo matāḥ",
    "T06n1333u_001:44": " ātmasnehātmamānātma - dṛṣṭināmavaśāt punaḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:45": " 20. etat trayaṃ hi tṛṣṇāyā - ātmamohavaśād bhavet",
    "T06n1333u_001:46": " tasmād avidyātṛṣṇātma - mohāḥ paryāyavācakāḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:47": " 21. etair jātās tu saṃskārā - na vidyante'rhate kvacit",
    "T06n1333u_001:48": " kliśyate sarvakāle tu - cittam etaiḥ pṛthagjane |",
    "T06n1333u_001:49": " 22. pāriśuddhiṃ hi cittasya - saṃskārakṣayam eva tat",
    "T06n1333u_001:50": " puṇyapāpaprahīṇasya - cittaṃ nirvutam ucyate |",
    "T06n1333u_001:51": " 23. prabhāsvaraṃ hi taccittam - anyat kliṣṭam bhavet sadā",
    "T06n1333u_001:52": " tasmāt pṛthagjanāḥ sarve - unmattā ityudīritāḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:53": " 24. yad vedayati tat sarvaṃ - saṃjānāti tathā punaḥ",
    "T06n1333u_001:54": " vitarkayati tajjñātaṃ - tad vitarkam prapañcayet |",
    "T06n1333u_001:55": " 25. ityuvāca mahārhā sa - kāśyapo manasaḥ kriyām",
    "T06n1333u_001:56": " nikāye madhyame pālyāṃ - sūtre tu madhupiṇḍike |",
    "T06n1333u_001:57": " 26. prapañco nāma saṃskāro - yāvad āharate phalam",
    "T06n1333u_001:58": " tāvad akriyavijñāna - rūpeṇaivāvatiṣṭhati |",
    "T06n1333u_001:59": " 27. karmasaṃskārasaṃkleśa - prapañcāśravakiñcanāḥ",
    "T06n1333u_001:60": " puṇyapāpe ca kuśalā - kuśaletīñjitāmalāḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:61": " 28. saṅgasaṃyojane śalyā - nuśayānuśravāśayāḥ",
    "T06n1333u_001:62": " upādānānganāḥ kleśāḥ - sarve paryāyavācakāḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:63": " 29. vedanāsaṃjñāyugalaṃ - sasaṃskāratrikañ ca yat",
    "T06n1333u_001:64": " vīthivijñānanāmena - kriyakarmavaśaj javet |",
    "T06n1333u_001:65": " 30. kriyaṃ hi vīthivijñānaṃ - nirvutāvyākṛtam bhavet",
    "T06n1333u_001:66": " karmabhūtaṃ vītthicittaṃ - vyākṛtañ cāpyanirvutam |",
    "T06n1333u_001:67": " 31. buddhārhatāṃ suddhacittaṃ - kriyarūpeṇa dhāvati",
    "T06n1333u_001:68": " pṛthagjanasya cittan tu - karmatatvena dhāvayet |",
    "T06n1333u_001:69": " 32. puṇyapāpaprahīṇaṃ yat - suddhaṃ buddhasya mānasam",
    "T06n1333u_001:70": " taddhi lokottaraṃ jñātam-nāsti tasya punarbhavaḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:71": " 33. bhavāṅgajaṃ vīthicittaṃ - cakṣurādikrameṇa ṣaṭ",
    "T06n1333u_001:72": " tadālambavaśāt tacca - vīthimuktam praviśyati |",
    "T06n1333u_001:73": " 34. kiryacittaṃ karmacittaṃ - dvayaṃ vīthiṃ pracakṣate",
    "T06n1333u_001:74": " vīthimuktan tu vijñānaṃ - vīthicittaiḥ pravardhate |",
    "T06n1333u_001:75": " 35. vipākākriyavijñānaṃ - pratisandhir bhaved bhave",
    "T06n1333u_001:76": " bhavāṅgam pravṛttau bhūtvā - jīvitānte bhaveccyutiḥ |",
    "T06n1333u_001:77": " 36. mūlavijñānam ālaya - vijñānam iti nāmake",
    "T06n1333u_001:78": " buddhavijñānaśabdārthe - vasubandhuḥ prayūyujat |",
    "T06n1333u_001:79": " 37. bhavam bhavāṅgam tatsroto - vijñānam eva bhāvayet",
    "T06n1333u_001:80": " pratisandhicyutībhyāṃ tad - vīthimuktaṃ prakīrtitam |",
    "T06n1333u_001:81": " 38. kriyabhūtaṃ karmabhūtaṃ - vīthicittaṃ dvidhā matam",
    "T06n1333u_001:82": " akriyaṃ vīthimuktaṃ vai - vipākam eva sarvadā |",
    "T06n1333u_001:83": " 39. sakarmaṃ vīthicittan tu - buddhādiṣu na vidyate",
    "T06n1333u_001:84": " teṣāṃ hi vīthicittaṃ vai - kriyarūpeṇa dhāvati |",
    "T06n1333u_001:85": " 40. āryāṣṭāṅgikamārgeṇa - karmakṣayakṛtam manaḥ",
    "T06n1333u_001:86": " buddhānām arhatañ caiva - nāhvayate punarbhavam |",
    "T06n1333u_001:87": " 41. kriyākarmavipākais tu - sarvaṃ cittaṃ vibhāvyate",
    "T06n1333u_001:88": " vedanāsaṃjñāsaṃskāra - vijñānaiś ca tathaiva tat |",
    "T06n1333u_001:89": " 42. pratītyasamutpādākhye - dharme deśitavedanā",
    "T06n1333u_001:90": " saṃjñārthaṃ vedanārthañ ca - dvayam eva prakāśate |",
    "T06n1333u_001:91": " 43. trīṇyevārthāni cittasya - prayogasya vaśāt punaḥ",
    "T06n1333u_001:92": " mūladvaitīyasāmānya - nāmais tattrikam ucyate |",
    "T06n1333u_001:93": " 44. mūlārtho hi tu cittasya - vedanārtham prakāśate",
    "T06n1333u_001:94": " vedanaṃ tasminnarthe tu - buddha eva prayūyujat |",
    "T06n1333u_001:95": " 45. dvaitīyārthan tu cittasya - saṃjñārtham eva bhāvayet",
    "T06n1333u_001:96": " sāmānyārtho hi tasya syāt - cittaṃ vāthonam aṅgikam |",
    "T06n1333u_001:97": " 46. tathaiva ca manaśśabdas - tadevārthatrayaṃ dadet",
    "T06n1333u_001:98": " mūlārthaṃ hi bhavet saṃjñā - dvaitīyārthaṃ tu vedanā",
    "T06n1333u_001:99": " sāmānyārtho manaśśabde - cittayuktasamo bhavet |",
    "T06n1333u_001:100": " 47. vedanāsaṃjñā saṃskāra - vijñānānāṃ yathākramam",
    "T06n1333u_001:101": " antargatārthān manasaś - cittasyaivañ ca jñāyatām |",
    "T06n1333u_001:102": " 48. vijñānam eva vijñaptiḥ - kriyākriyavaśā dvidhā",
    "T06n1333u_001:103": " vijñaptimātratā siddhā - cittasyaivaṃ hi niścayāt |",
    "T06n1333u_001:104": " 49. kṣaṇajanyā ca vijñaptir - anityā kṣaṇabhangurā",
    "T06n1333u_001:105": " tadātmakesmiṃś citte tu - māyā syād ātmakalpanā |",
    "T06n1333u_001:106": " 50. pratītyasamutpāde ca - pañcaskandhe ca darśane",
    "T06n1333u_001:107": " vidyamānam cittatatvaṃ - samyag evaṃ prakāśitam |",
    "T06n1333u_001:108": " śrī lankāputrabhūtena - paṇḍitācāryabhikṣuṇā",
    "T06n1333u_001:109": " āmerikādharmadūta - priyanandena dhīmatā",
    "T06n1333u_001:110": " vijñaptimātrātasiddhi - pañcāśiketi nāmikā",
    "T06n1333u_001:111": " kṛtaivaṃ kṛ tir eṣā tu - cittatatvasya saṅgrahaḥ |"
}